author: johnh
msg: End-to-end support for supportDefer="true" in ExportJsProcessor
Also includes all/new/loaded feature computation in JsRequest, as a useful convenience.

This CL adds support for the supportDefer="true" annotation in <api>. In its presence, the exportJs() calls generated by ExportJsProcessor are augmented to request deferred symbol binding when &jsload=1. This in turn allows support for synchronously enqueueing requests to symbols whose full implementations haven't yet been loaded.
